{"type": "article", "id": 28271, "title": "可以发光的积木", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-16T06:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021622588FL1WYvonb0NXz6K.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你也曾梦想过让自己搭成的积木模型变成一盏灯，LIGHT STAX 设计团队推出的这套可以发光的积木玩具就能满足你的心愿。LIGHT STAX 本身是一套有多种颜色的透明积木，点亮的奥秘在于名为 Power STAX 的一块特殊积木：它自带 USB 接口和开关，连上电源后将它与透明积木拼接在一起，其他积木就会通过磁力逐渐被点亮。每块 Power STAX 最多可以点亮 500 块积木，内置的 LED 灯还提供三种不同的点亮方式，让你打造一个独一无二的装饰灯。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/brandtraders/light-stax-toy-bricks-meet-led\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 15 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162256IToCRKutFJDGzL89.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162257lzUOuHZI5hr3A19m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.459375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162257DcmOuBvHkXTwLxp4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162258Lsz8OuHIdR4BCEZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}